txt.en: Embroidered 'Battle of the Field of Celebrant' Tapestry[v]

An embroidered tapestry depicting the Eorl's victory over the foes of Gondor.\n\nThe Tailor's Guild leader will accept this in exchange for a Sealed Westemnet Device of Battle, Accuracy, Tactics, Insight, Protection or Potency.
Embroidered 'Battle of the Field of Celebrant' Tapestries[p]
